# EasyMall 后端环境变量配置示例
# 复制为 .env 并填入实际值：cp .env.example .env
# 启动时指定 profile：--spring.profiles.active=prod

# ===== 应用配置 =====
SERVER_PORT=8080
SPRING_PROFILES_DEFAULT=prod
LOG_LEVEL=info
LOG_LEVEL_SECURITY=warn

# ===== MySQL 配置（必需）=====
SPRING_DATASOURCE_URL=jdbc:mysql://localhost:3306/easymall?useUnicode=true&characterEncoding=utf-8&useSSL=false&serverTimezone=UTC&allowPublicKeyRetrieval=true
SPRING_DATASOURCE_USERNAME=root
SPRING_DATASOURCE_PASSWORD=your_mysql_password

# ===== Redis 配置（必需）=====
SPRING_DATA_REDIS_HOST=localhost
# SPRING_DATA_REDIS_PORT=6379
SPRING_DATA_REDIS_PASSWORD=
# SPRING_DATA_REDIS_DATABASE=0

# ===== RabbitMQ 配置 =====
SPRING_RABBITMQ_HOST=localhost
# SPRING_RABBITMQ_PORT=5672
SPRING_RABBITMQ_USERNAME=guest
SPRING_RABBITMQ_PASSWORD=guest
# SPRING_RABBITMQ_VIRTUAL_HOST=/

# ===== 安全配置（必需）=====
JWT_SECRET=your_jwt_secret_key_at_least_256_bits_long
# JWT_EXPIRATION=86400000

# ===== 文件上传 =====
FILE_UPLOAD_BASE_PATH=/data/easymall/uploads
FILE_UPLOAD_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8080/uploads

# ===== 支付配置（必需）=====
PAYMENT_MOCK_SIGNATURE=your_mock_payment_signature

# ===== 业务配置 =====
# EASYMALL_ORDER_TIMEOUT_MINUTES=30
